author: ashtipliyski
body: PR includes logic to the CALOL2 event-by-event comparisons in Online DQM which should properly handle the exclusion from global running of Calo Layer 2 sub-system of the L1Trigger. This PR will be followed by backports to 93X and 92X (currently used in production).
title: Add logic to handle exclusion of CALOL2 in DQM
